ISLAMABAD, Apr 17 (APP):President Dr Arif Alvi will hold a consultative meeting with Ulema on Saturday regarding offering of congregational prayers and Namaz-e-Taraweeh at mosques during the month of Ramazan.
The meeting will formulate a strategy for effective steps to control the epidemic of COVID-19, the President House said.
